Restore perl-5.6 compatiblity.



_______________________________________________________________________________
2011-02-27 LWP-MediaTypes 6.01

Use mockup object to avoid test dependency on URI::URL and HTTP::Request.

Drop MacOS (classic) support



_______________________________________________________________________________
2011-02-25 LWP-MediaTypes 6.00

Initial release of LWP-MediaTypes as a separate distribution. There are no code
changes besides incrementing the version number since libwww-perl-5.837.

The LWP::MediaTypes module used to be bundled with the libwww-perl distribution.
